cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the task of machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a framework that utilizes a pretrained model to improve simultaneous translation. Additionally, it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural machine translation and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves natural language processing.
